-- Mets Beat Padres 11-2 in MLB Opener Behind Cowgill's Grand Slam
-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 2013-04-01T20:17:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-01/mets-beat-padres-11-2-in-mlb-opener-behind-cowgill-s-grand-slam.html
Collin Cowgill hit a grand slam and
Jon Niese gave up two runs in 6 2/3 innings as the  New York Mets 
opened their Major League Baseball season with an 11-2 victory
over the San Diego Padres.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
